license: MIT

abstract: >
  A location-aware GIS–LLM system for urban and transportation analysis,
  integrating map-based spatial grounding, MCP tool calling,
  and graph neural network representations of transportation networks
  for improved spatial reasoning and reduced spatial hallucinations.

